text:
Maryse is throwing down the gauntlet! Things get heated on the season seven premiere of Total Divas Wednesday night. New Divas star Nia Jax is prepping for her first Gauntlet match and makes the mistake of asking Maryse the wrong question. Let’s just say she better put some respect on her name!

Read more: http://www.eonline.com/shows/total_divas/news/889997/maryse-demands-some-respect-from-nia-jax-on-total-divas-season-premiere-see-their-heated-fight
